name: Validate all the fields exist in pop up

steps.name: the user is in Login Page
the user enters the username "playwrightuser@gmail.com" and "Playwright@1234"
the user navigates to the Dashboard page and get the title for verification
Given Admin is on the Dashboard page
When Admin clicks Batch on the Menu from the header
When the admin able to click edit button for the batchName
When the admin enters "","Active","12" and click Save button in Batch module
Then the admin should see the error message "Batch Description is required."
